@startuml Sistem3tombolSync_Overall
' ============================================
' Diagram: Activity Overview — 3tombolSync
' Menunjukkan alur integrasi seluruh sistem
' dari boot hingga sync data ke HP.
' ============================================

title **Sistem 3tombolSync — Diagram Alir Keseluruhan**

|User|
|Sensor & OLED|
|Sistem (3tombolSync.ino)|
|Earphone / HP|

|User|
start
:Colok batrai / Tekan OK\n(alat menyala);

|Sistem|
:BOOT: Cek reset reason\n— Power-on / Crash / Wake —;
if (Crash > 3x?) then (ya)
  :ENTER SAFE MODE\nTampil error di OLED;
  stop
else (tidak)
endif

:POWER ON: MOSFET aktif\nOLED init + LittleFS mount;

:Load waktu dari RTC/NVS;
:Init sensor:\n■ StepSensor (MPU6050)\n■ BreathSensor (ADC);
note right
  Kode Anda MEMANGGIL:
  stepSensor.begin()
  breathSensor.begin()
  Tapi algoritma deteksi ada
  di file terpisah (kode teman)
end note

:Init battery (MAX17048)
+ register callback;

|Sistem|
if (Boot mode?) then (SYNC)
  :BLE SERVICE ON\nAdvertising "Cheaststrap";
else (AUDIO / Normal)
  :A2DP SOURCE ON\nSiap streaming audio;
endif

|User|
:Scan & Pair Earphone (A2DP);
|Sistem|
:A2DP CONNECTED → reset state;
|User|
:Pilih Pola Napas:\n■ 3:2 (RELAX)\n■ 2:1 (POWER);
|Sistem|
:STATE_IDLE — siap menerima langkah;

|User|
:Mulai berlari;
|Sensor & OLED|
:LANGKAH terdeteksi\n(MPU6050 → StepSensor);
|Sistem|
:handleStepAnalysis():
■ Hitung SPM, T_avg
■ Cek stabilitas (stable_count)
■ 5 langkah stabil → STATE_GUIDING;

|Sistem|
if (Pertama kali GUIDING?) then (ya)
  :RECORDING MULAI
  ■ Catat recording_start_ms
  ■ Tulis SESSION header ke /run.dat
  ■ naikkan session_id;
else (tidak)
  :RESUME recording\n(lanjut sesi yang sama);
endif

|Sistem|
:SCHEDULING AUDIO CUE:
■ Hitung time_to_trigger
  = N×T_avg − (T_LEAD + L_SYS)
■ ARM esp_timer;

|Sensor & OLED|
:NAPAS terdeteksi\n(ADC → BreathSensor);
|Sistem|
:Breath phase diterima\n(1 = HIRUP, -1 = BUANG);

|Sistem|
:WRITE LOG ENTRY:\n[ts_ms | flags | spm]\n→ 6 byte biner → /run.dat;

|Earphone / HP|
:Audio cue HIRUP/BUANG\nterdengar di earphone;

|Sistem|
:OLED UPDATE:
■ Status: GUIDING >>
■ SPM, Volume, *REC;

|Sistem|
while (User masih lari?) is (ya)
  :Langkah berikutnya → loop;
  if (>3 langkah meleset?) then (ya)
    :RECORDING PAUSE
    ■ Audio HENING (guard!)
    ■ OLED: Status ANALYZING;
    if (Ritme stabil lagi?) then (ya)
      :RESUME recording;
    else (tidak)
      :Tunggu stabil...;
    endif
  endif
endwhile (Tidak)

|User|
:Selesai lari / Tombol mati;
|Sistem|
:ENTER DEEP SLEEP:
■ Flush & close /run.dat
■ Simpan waktu ke RTC+NVS
■ MOSFET OFF
■ ESP.restart() → deep sleep path;

|User|
:Pilih menu SYNC (long-press OK);
|Sistem|
:Ganti boot mode → SYNC;
:ESP.restart() → BLE mode;

|Sistem|
:BLE ADVERTISING;
|User|
:Buka aplikasi Flutter di HP;
:Tap SYNC;
|Sistem|
:Terima "SYNC" dari HP;

|Sistem|
:BACA /run.dat → konversi BINER→CSV:
■ 0xFF = SESSION header
■ Record 6-byte → csvLine;

|Earphone / HP|
:Kirim CSV via BLE Notify:
■ Header → data chunked (350 char)
■ EOF → tunggu ACK;

|Earphone / HP|
:HP parse data → kirim "OK";
|Sistem|
:ACK diterima → HAPUS /run.dat;
:Selesai → kembali ke AUDIO mode;

stop
@enduml